<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٨٢٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6768">‌وَاصِلُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْأَعْلَى </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5879">‌ابْنِ فُضَيْلٍ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">‌الْأَعْمَشِ </a>بِهَذَا قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَأَنَّهُ يُحِبُّ الْجَمَاعَةَ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>